{"tid":1723910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果大家仲想贏 請正視態度問題","createTime":"2019-11-15T10:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T18:11:16.000Z","uid":63639,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a86c52377e5002c435c6e7fcae2d77d64730cf36","tid":1723910,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"今個星期發起嘅黎明行動確實成功打破部份關口 <br />\n早上多區行動令班曱甴由朝做到晚 <br />\n完全係唔洗休息 好明顯睇到佢地已經係搞唔掂<br />\n<br />\n但同時亦發生咗好多事 包括<br />\n\t1.\tCU 被代表記者會<br />\n\t2.\tPOLYU 捉鬼+ 被批評態度問題<br />\n\t3.\t上水被懷疑裝修錯（自己友）店問題<br />\n<br />\n係一個無大台模式運作嘅革命下<br />\n我哋需要接受係會有出錯<br />\n但係錯嘅時候 <span style=\"color: red;\">我哋係唔應該扮睇唔到 <br />\n相反應該為咗我哋嘅錯誤承擔責任 改善下一次 </span><br />\n<br />\n我哋之前已經講過 <br />\n有<span style=\"color: red;\">基本嘅紀律係我哋同班曱甴唔同嘅地方</span> <br />\n有幾樣嘢我希望大家可以留意￼<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割蓆 不督灰</span></span>: <br />\n手足做錯左嘅時候￼￼￼ 商討改善方法 下次唔好再錯 <br />\n<br />\n2. ￼￼<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be humble 友善提醒 虛心接納</span></span> : <br />\n打緊仗 大壓力休息唔夠￼ 係好正常 <br />\n但希望大家留意 身邊每一個都係手足 <br />\n態度好少少￼￼ 友善咁提出問題 虛心接納其他人意見<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">存在底線</span></span>: <br />\n以上水藥房被裝修為例<br />\n睇返老細六月時嘅post￼￼￼￼ 其實好明顯佢係一個和理非 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係黃</span></span> 可能當時手足搞錯咗 <br />\n我哋唔會割 但我哋必須共同承擔責任<br />\n我哋唔可以因為佢賣水貨就裝修￼ 咁樣同打壓政見係一樣￼ 相反 我哋必須向老細致歉<br />\n(即使老細話唔需要籌款) 依個先係真正需要展現我哋同極權政府唔同態度嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 請記得: 政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己 而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己 改變想法 認同自己的方向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"54c44da5855c8fc4f2c6bd921cdbb294f8ba3fc9","tid":1723910,"uid":210254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ded19f5bf103ab0d70e935c716e43ccc5c38b74a","tid":1723910,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b2d72dae1907045568ce63d702181048e0fdef","tid":1723910,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acb4c07eac15fe166d4821e534b6dabda52151b","tid":1723910,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:22:09.000Z","msg":"推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef58c9f7227623a1e15fa6cda9e0a176c550ac73","tid":1723910,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"推4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46a73d052710a8dba454cc70f84b78cbab9e365","tid":1723910,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"推4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e5198f23f4b5bae4df05f0ed63712c00369729","tid":1723910,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"推5<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ec892